  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄물 소량, 디자인에서부터</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-82112ab2-e0dd-4d17-9818-edcc82619109\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4b79af92-5ddc-4cd3-a8ed-249a4f74b8b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄 자동견적 솔루션</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0eb4af26-5402-47c6-bb95-2516f56c2845\" style=\"color:#555555;\">까지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bb4fb7cc-ee2c-4484-8479-39f6c071a7d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6ab8b9eb-69f4-4286-b1ab-5b37599e4c75\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c0c91ee2-a736-43cf-959b-ab26aa6cf7a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">의</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1fcdd53e-6368-4f5a-aa5f-0f73414b5371\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> 모든 것</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c0451440-a4ed-4777-986b-54d8834fc5c9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223763858066/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6fb415a9-8639-456b-bac9-97b5a01d9acf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:415px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223763858066/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b1835686-75af-4d14-9a9d-bdd207106ce6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223763858066/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ecbf6959-6478-4b88-9d1c-e80f2cab22ce\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0563dc2a-fc2e-45c0-a857-9b82b987e2b5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c3969ba1-e904-4ae2-ba98-bf35089f4bbb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음과 같은 행택이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-34ff340a-0dc8-4929-8063-3693eeb92a43\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2d9afae-46da-4610-af08-1945c14caa00\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인이 헷갈리게 되어 있는 업체가 많습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니의 가이드는 간단합니다. 도무송되는 칼선과 작업의 여백사이즈만 숙지하시고 주문하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2fd1e495-7a07-4e57-aa0a-ab5ea20db79f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25a7c183-871b-4457-85bd-9246aa3a74fb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-5e0c0559-6af6-4acd-9d0d-ab4410b2c33d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c31a3603-6a9f-4f36-9cb3-c1f8692e235c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-28d05b46-8584-4166-b4b9-381f7ed52a11\" style=\"\">행택의 구성</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-09c41adb-cde1-4a4e-bf61-155040a81713\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-575814c9-e1ef-4326-88f5-fbd063d52108\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7693eb13-01b4-428b-b6d5-3a2c8a0cb963\" style=\"color:#555555;\">행택은 다음과 같은 구성요소를 가지고 있습니다. 잘 보시고 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-af77a04a-e32c-4195-b9a3-67b5cf6508e6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">주문 시 사고가 나지 않도록 조심</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d2b25bb-8164-4cb1-a04c-fc0748b0ae67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ae9e1174-5cad-4289-9c84-cd899d4d8a4f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223763858066/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f6c5aa7-6012-4141-bf2a-ace919c03f34\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed16cf58-d54b-436c-a481-499038887eb4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-136acab1-236e-4b85-9f5a-0ec4043c9e8a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ddb52d22-7a6e-446f-ba04-115269ca8a09\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86c43ea6-f17e-4911-85d3-a2766e4c9d01\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가장 저렴한 스노우지에서부터 수입지까지 특별하게 가능합니다. 또한 더 두꺼운 행택을 원할 시에는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fdba91c7-36f6-411b-ac65-058f333e26ca\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>합지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-25af0a9a-32ef-4162-bc8b-1f05172e47ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">를 해서 더 두껍게도 제작하는 경우가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a7d7e731-e816-4dd7-9bb0-9bd0353de464\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9576c917-8c94-43ba-a60f-e043f762cadb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb7af06e-a01b-492b-8b5d-9cc3a4e57b7d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a79d1254-9b06-4a30-b40a-e34e7dc45b3f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c1d8bff5-e9a4-43fc-a44a-3a1d29ad8251\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-721b274f-a4d3-42e5-997a-43e0464e06b5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">행택인쇄는 양면인쇄로 제작되는 것이 기본입니다. 특별한 경우에만 단면 인쇄가 되지만 인쇄비의 차이가 많지 않기에 양면으로 디자인을 많이 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0dfece45-d4d6-4781-a9d4-6105edeccc7c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f178b643-66f1-4376-90b6-92b874fbbbe7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7696b1c3-83e2-419d-984e-5c4e199910b1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1bd7c035-f6f3-4c2f-87fd-32d143c6342e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>도무송(톰슨)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-812a78d2-7023-41f1-b65d-c38cad3e85e1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b49c645-5ba0-436b-9913-345dfc01cd7e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">행택의 모양은 기본형이 있지만 자유롭게 디자인해도 무방합니다. 거의 대부분 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2198d2ed-c52a-4daa-8834-66d9cf63786e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디지털 커팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-54a863ea-4ad4-40d2-9939-85ad30faebc5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">으로 제작이 되므로 조금의 비용을 추가하여 자유로운 모양으로 디자인해 주셔도 됩니다. 문의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6652683f-047e-48e0-8996-a748b1ebc903\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d173a649-8319-4087-9d09-3125f95fc423\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2eba050f-ebed-4ea8-b382-7707d28dd72d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-412c756f-588e-4802-909e-22149b8fa7c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>부자재</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a6bd8d79-7c03-48e1-84f2-7a572b59ecd0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9321866a-4229-47cd-95dc-0efa37d4ea66\" style=\"color:#555555;\">부자재는 실과 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d3f3cf76-d02f-4574-bc3e-f52aa61c801c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>아일렛</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1e103ab-b2f3-4fb1-8055-50e030bc6a4f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">등이 있을 수 있습니다. 물론 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2a2d1b97-9828-4fc6-b6fb-19ab0743cada\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>타공</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c5253157-1b0f-4f91-b15b-d3201f5feba8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만 하면 단가를 줄일 수 있지만 아일렛으로 더 독특하게 처리하는 행택도 많습니다. 아일렛 하나가 버려지는 행택일지 몰라도 조금 더 제품을 고급스럽게 보일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1027257-af99-4490-8af3-3a74e0f015ee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa79a964-9c56-463a-8716-2dc68168be00\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ac1443c5-22c0-4ef2-9c9b-4ed75c376ca9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3708d53e-5eac-41c4-bc4f-dd07e10abb46\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또한 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-84781049-291a-4e90-83c5-e0aa122d5cc8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>실</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9fb65884-0305-468f-81bc-a8937db1b755\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 또한 기본 색상은 검은색이지만 브랜드 색상에 맞는 색상으로 처리할 수 있습니다. 물론 비용이 추가로 발행하고 그 처리가 복잡하여 납기도 늦어질 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-415a6fdd-670c-4ae5-b7a5-3e13ccc5ef70\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223763858066/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b7b690be-2059-4e88-8a80-08045e08d19b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5df59a01-1915-474b-8c0c-0a9ed1c8f637\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b7bd90b1-d3f8-450a-991f-82f255f4b806\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위의 행택처럼 접지형으로 작업도 가능합니다. 양쪽에 타공을 처리하여 슬을 엇갈려 끼웁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-2b9170ee-3ac8-42c6-9090-43d90467cdea\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-0cbbbf82-b3f6-4bf3-9384-a4a67f1efae4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cbc71f16-ca22-4304-af28-ef105c3c4985\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-11db3ce5-d69b-471f-be5d-d781a13956d2\" style=\"\">디자인은 다음과 같이 하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-844e193f-66ad-45ee-9230-24e0d7430f2d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b1f8fa3-96f0-485c-9b6f-b355ef369a03\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de75899a-9069-4ec9-b5d7-d3d9d2c39173\" style=\"color:#555555;\">행택 디자인은 다음과 같은 가이드로 작업하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0dd88067-a581-488f-be0d-d2fa6288170b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223763858066/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1c9f10e9-b4e9-4510-868a-e71fb8278af7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be79b0cb-0b4d-474c-9f92-f9bf9ca14db3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ababa904-3b78-4053-a95f-ecab029bb920\" style=\"color:#555555;\">작업선과 행택 도무송(톰슨)선을 잘 판단하세요. 작은 사이즈이니 만큼 공간의 여백이 많습니다. 또한 작업 시에는 반드시 문의를 주시고 (주)파파스컴퍼니 칼선을 받아서 작업하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-43cc36b0-3632-4c2d-9b33-91f834f113c0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-19232ed7-b1ee-49e8-96da-1be73f72b899\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0b825a39-f4b9-445e-9891-56250c605fce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b886317d-ec16-40e4-9270-b35119c0e936\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 여러 번 강조했지만 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-579d71da-166d-48e0-a3e1-7c651ae6fabe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>친절한 설명</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e36ec31f-686a-43ca-8804-e78ceada9f6d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 모토로 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8ff505de-cf3d-41ca-8d88-969de0bc2f5c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7221956c-0ddf-4d1c-9e1d-504808a4713b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c595eea-aa31-4c5e-8112-2fb26b9d7407\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ae40521-e5cd-40a2-b8b1-f0a8c85677f7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 분은 바로 문의주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b34c95d9-2603-4466-af47-15777f763bee\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-19ec69df-ed28-4538-aa28-1f64f1da22a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-61461677-006c-4913-a3fa-1b20a92f989a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-23e82185-6020-4b87-b144-4122d6f7aee7\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">소량으로 의류 부자재를 제작하고 싶은 소상공인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-884c86f4-e462-4fa6-bb81-dd7b9bffb81a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2274848b-7408-4ea0-a416-ffdc58852fd3\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e9b167b5-9fa2-48ec-ac57-dc1cec6e2f98\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0ee381f-f4f0-4221-b41d-1abc7df5bcb0\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">나만의 제품을 온라인으로 판매하지만 대량생산을 하지 못하는 특수 제조업체</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c36a29b8-961a-45c8-b9ec-a85fc6380510\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2f3f0e6b-5547-4381-bd18-b4e20dde1b6e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b5f8680c-2f4d-4a4f-b995-5c09db2e69a6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e9301354-fc0d-43d6-99a6-67b79bc576ea\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">일반적인 행택이 아닌 브랜드가 가미된 특별하고 고급스러운 디자인 행택을 원하는 고객</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8cdbf821-e76a-49fc-8048-bb18da22fc6c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b4290a0d-4b0e-4755-92f8-b06c0ff5a342\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34807bed-b651-4812-bbf2-92890f5e77eb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2ec29a07-aa68-40ab-af58-2b390d1d543d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffe3c8;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 주문으로 이어지지 않으셔도 관계없습니다. 주문이나 발주를 떠나 인쇄 전반에 대해 궁금하신 상황이나 인쇄사고를 여러 번 경함하신 고객님의 상담을 환영합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd909f85-21a6-4a63-9f5a-7973a886f388\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1b4d0f99-e7a9-4377-84f9-5efef2461f03\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6007bdd3-719c-4847-aa59-df2515898c80\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-23d19932-3e4f-49be-af4d-c4cbc781ef95\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#9bdfff;\"><b>편하게 문의주세요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b3fc74dd-c7fc-47d9-9c46-2c8719db4249\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}